headline: Is Linde (LIN) Pricing In Too Much Future Growth After Strong Multi Year Run?
summary: If you are wondering whether Linde’s current share price reflects its true worth, you are not alone. This article is built to help you connect the recent share moves with what the underlying valuation actually suggests. Linde’s stock closed at US$459.69, with returns of 0.6% over the past week, 5.9% over the past month, 7.1% year to date, 2.4% over one year, 44.0% over three years and 94.9% over five years. This naturally raises questions about how much of the story is already priced...
